#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you have more than one version of &kde; installed (e.g. &kde;2 and "
#~ "&kde;3), this may possibly install &konsolekalendar; into the wrong &kde; "
#~ "folder. If necessary, you can give the &kde; folder as a parameter to "
#~ "<userinput><command>./configure</command></userinput>. For example, if "
#~ "your &kde; is installed in <filename>/opt/kde3</filename>:"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Si vous avez plusieurs versions de &kde; sur votre ordinateur (&pex;, "
#~ "&kde;2 et &kde;3), cette commande est susceptible d'installer "
#~ "&konsolekalendar; dans le mauvais dossier &kde;. Si nécessaire, attribuez "
#~ "au dossier &kde; un paramètre à <userinput><command>./configure</"
#~ "command></userinput>. Par exemple, si votre &kde; est installé dans "
#~ "<filename>/opt/kde3</filename> :"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<command>./configure</command> --prefix=<replaceable>/opt/kde3</"
#~ "replaceable>"
#~ msgstr ""
